Step 1 :
Launch i-pi by typing:
${PATH2IPI}/bin/i-pi input.xml > log.i-pi & 

Step 2 :
Launch LAMMPS by typing:
${PATH2LAMMPS}/src/${LMP_EXE} < in.lmp > log.lmp & 

Step 3 :
Wait for the calculation to end.
Run the post processing script to get the free energy:
${PATH2IPI}/tools/py/get_Ascp.pu -i input.xml > log.scp 

Step 4 : 
Plot the anharmonic free energy:
gnuplot > p "log.scp" us 1:2 w l 
